<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{% include "head.njk" %}

<body class="home-page">
  {% include "header.njk" %}

  <main>
    <section id="hero" class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-overlay">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1 class="hero-heading">Beyond words, In Tune with your authentic self</h1>
          <p class="hero-subheading">Clinical music therapy sessions to support your mental health and emotional well-being</p>
          <a href="/contact/" class="hero-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>









    <section id="services" class="services-section">
      <div class="services-grid">
        <!-- Large Music Therapy Services Card -->
        <a href="/services/" class="services-card services-card-large"
          style="background-image: url('images/pictures/johannes-plenio-RWytwNueNng-unsplash.jpg');">
          <div class="services-card-content">
            <h2>Music Therapy Services</h2>
            <p>
              Experience creative, evidence-based therapy tailored to your goals — 
              a space to explore and heal beyond words. <br> Click to Learn More
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Also Offering Heading -->
        <h3 class="services-subheading">Also Offering...</h3>

        <!-- Two Sub-Cards Row -->
        <div class="services-row">

          <a href="/professionals/" class="services-card"
            style="background-image: url('images/pictures/pexels-pavel-danilyuk-7120394.jpg');">
            <div class="services-card-content">
              <h2>Clinical Supervision</h2>
              <p>
                Support for music therapists seeking growth, guidance, and reflective 
                practice in a creative, affirming space. <br> Click to Learn More
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/professionals/" class="services-card"
            style="background-image: url('images/pictures/headway-5QgIuuBxKwM-unsplash.jpg');">
            <div class="services-card-content">
              <h2>Consultation</h2>
              <p>
                Professional collaboration for providers, clinics, or programs 
                exploring music therapy and mental health. <br> Click to Learn More
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>










    <section id="problem" class="problem-section">
      <div class="problem-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Does this sound like you?</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Here are the common problems people bring to music therapy — so you know we're familiar with what you're going through.</p>

        <div class="problem-grid" role="list">
          <article class="problem-card" role="listitem" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="p1-title">
            <div class="parallelogram">
              <div class="card-inner">
                <h3 id="p1-title">Self awareness isn't translating into relief</h3>
                <p>You're highly aware of what's going wrong in your life, maybe you've even been called an "over-intellectualizer", or have a lot of insight- but you're still stuck.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="problem-card" role="listitem" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="p2-title">
            <div class="parallelogram">
              <div class="card-inner">
                <h3 id="p2-title">Talking about it isn't getting to the core of the issue</h3>
                <p>Words aren't enough- traditional talk therapy doesn't give you the tools tools you actually need.  Music can go where words cannot.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="problem-card" role="listitem" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="p3-title">
            <div class="parallelogram">
              <div class="card-inner">
                <h3 id="p3-title">Masking is starting to cost you</h3>
                <p>You feel misunderstood or alienated by traditional therapy.  You crave something predictable yet novel to work through the stress of life.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="meet">
      <div class="meet-container">
        <div class="meet-columns">
          <div class="meet-image">
            <img src="images/pictures/mk_self_portrait.png" alt="Makenzie smiling" />
          </div>

          <div class="meet-text">
            <h2><b>Meet Makenzie</b></h2>
            <hr />
            <h2>Board Certified Music Therapist</h2>
            <p>
              I bring warmth, validation, and creativity to every session. With over 15 years of experience 
              and a foundation in Dialectical Behavior Therapy, I've used Music Therapy to support clients 
              through a wide range of mental health challenges. I provide affirming, compassionate, and 
              authentic care with humor, directness, curiosity, and heart.<br>
              I am an ally, anti-diet, as well as ENM and neurodivergence affirming.
            </p><br><br>
            <a href="/about/" class="learn-more-btn">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="why">
      <div class="why-music-therapy-section">
        <h2 class="hero-heading">Why Music Therapy?</h2>

        <div class="card-container">
          <!-- Full-width featured card -->
          <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card full-span">
            <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Embody Your Authentic Self</h3>
            <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
              Music therapy provides a space transcendent to words to explore emotion, identity, and the self, especially when the truth is beyond words.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Grid of smaller cards -->
          <div class="grid-wrapper">
            <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card">
              <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Regulate Emotions</h3>
              <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
                The path of music through the brain involves the emotion center twice. Music deeply affects emotions.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card">
              <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Increase Self-Awareness</h3>
              <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
                Learn more about your authentic self through music therapy experiences.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card">
              <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Strengthen Relationships</h3>
              <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
                Explore connection with yourself or others through the therapeutic process.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card">
              <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Process Trauma</h3>
              <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
                Access non-verbal pathways to heal safely.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card">
              <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Reduce Stress</h3>
              <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
                This isn't about just listening to a relaxation track. Use your music to get your stress level to where you want it to be.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="why-music-therapy-card rainbow-card">
              <h3 class="why-music-therapy-title">Increase Focus</h3>
              <p class="why-music-therapy-description">
                Music activates presence and cognitive clarity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

{% include "footer.njk" %}
<script src="js/navigation.js"></script>
<script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
